p://childrensworkshopschool.org/?page_id=718',0,'page','',0),(1364,1,'2014-08-31 18:46:03','2014-08-31 22:46:03','&nbsp;\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3><strong>...a progressive public elementary school located in the East Village of Manhattan. <a title=\"Contact\" href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/contact/\">We are located on 610 East 12th Street between Avenues B &amp; C.</a>For current parents, our most updated newsblasts moved to the <a title=\"ANNOUNCEMENTS\" href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/announcements/\">\"ANNOUNCEMENTS\" page</a>. Check back for more! And sign up for our email newsletters via <a title=\"Stay Connected\" href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/keepintouch/\">Email-Signups</a> to stay connected.</strong></h3>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Families interested in The Children’s Workshop School, </strong></span></h2>\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">please email Joyce </span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">(<a href=\"mailto:jborden@schools.nyc.gov\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">jborden@schools.nyc.gov</span></a>) or call Joyce at (212) 614-9531 Ext 2091to sign up for a school tour starting in late September. </span></span>\n\nAny questions about Pre-K admission for Fall 2015, or 2014 placements in other grades as well, please contact Joyce.We look forward to meeting you!<a title=\"School Tours\" href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/admissions/school-tours/\">Watch this spot for tours starting in September and Open House dates.</a>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">NEXT TOUR DATE: Tuesday, December 16th at 8:15am Meet in the LOBBY</span></h2>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"top\">\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">November 27-28, No School on Thanksgiving</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Monday, December 1st World AIDS Day March/Sing AlongFriday, December 12th Bookfair visits\n\nWednesday December 24 - Monday, January 5, WINTER RECESS</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<strong>Children\'s Workshop School strives</strong> for students to be open-minded and compassionate; to gain a sense of themselves and others; and to understand and appreciate the diversity of the community. Children are guided and supported to fulfill their creative, physical, emotional, social and intellectual potential. Our goal is for our children to recognize that they have the power and resources to effect change. It is our hope that children will grow to be responsible, critical and caring members of a pluralistic society.</td>\n<td align=\"top\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/welcome/craftfair14/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1466\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1466\" alt=\"CRAFTFAIR14\" src=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/CRAFTFAIR14-550x713.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"713\" /></a> <a href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/welcome/cws-winter-book-fair2rev/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1464\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1464\" alt=\"cws winter book fair2rev\" src=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/cws-winter-book-fair2rev-550x711.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"711\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>','WELCOME Children\'s Workshop School...','','publish','open','open','','welcome','','','2014-08-31 18:46:03','2014-08-31 22:46:03','',0,'http://childrensworkshopschool.org/?page_id=1364',0,'page','',0),(1368,1,'2014-08-31 19:05:04','2014-08-31 23:05:04','Of course you can read our <a title=\"ANNOUNCEMENTS\" href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/announcements/\">\"ANNOUNCEMENTS\" page</a> on a daily basis. In addition, to receive our email blasts, please sign up through the form below.\n\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n\n	<link href=\"//cdn-images.mailchimp.com/embedcode/classic-081711.css\" r